				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$y \in \mathbb {R}$$\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M120"><mml:mrow><mml:mi>y</mml:mi><mml:mo>&#x02208;</mml:mo><mml:mi mathvariant="double-struck">R</mml:mi></mml:mrow></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="11538_2018_415_Article_IEq54.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula>, is given by<disp-formula id="Equ8"><label>8</label><alternatives><tex-math id="M121">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
