				\begin{document}$$\varvec{x}_i\in {\mathcal {Y}}$$\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M1064"><mml:mrow><mml:msub><mml:mrow><mml:mi mathvariant="bold-italic">x</mml:mi></mml:mrow><mml:mi>i</mml:mi></mml:msub><mml:mo>&#x02208;</mml:mo><mml:mi mathvariant="script">Y</mml:mi></mml:mrow></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="11538_2018_415_Article_IEq466.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula> satisfy the condition <inline-formula id="IEq467"><alternatives><tex-math id="M1065">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
